VALUES
	(3029, 1042, 857, 1042, 1314, 1, 'Holotropic Breathwork Australia', 'holotropic-breathwork-australia', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large with-redo row-columns-1-1 has-section-width-uk-container\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-1@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p></p></div>\n                        </div>                    <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h4>Looking for a Holotropic Breathwork Workshop in Australia. This site holds all of the upcoming workshops for accredited <a href=\"https://holotropic.com.au\">Holotropic Breathwork workshop facilitators in Australia</a>.</h4></div>\n                        </div></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            \n            \n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2020-11-18 06:52:00', NULL, 0, '1', 'https://www.holtropic.com.au', 'nikola-majksner-hXNGeAFOgT4-unsplash_n3h12u', 1042, 1, 'Looking for a Holotropic Breathwork Workshop in Australia. This site holds all of the upcoming workshops for accredited Holotropic Breathwork workshop facilitators in Australia.', 'Accredited Holotropic Breathwork Workshops in Australia', NULL, 'Discover upcoming Holotropic Breathwork workshops in Australia. Join our accredited facilitators for a transformative experience.', '2025-07-10 07:56:07', '2026-01-05 00:10:30', 4, NULL, 63, NULL, 0, 60, NULL, 1, ''),
	(3030, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'Discover Your Inner Healer: A Guide to Holistic Healing and Breathwork', 'discover-your-inner-healer-a-guide-to-holistic-healing-and-breathwork', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative redactor-component-active\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span class=\"redactor-component-caret\">﻿</span>\n                                    <img class=\"fb-image-white-border-large\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/q_70/f_auto/r_0/1314/meagan-carsience-TpG2TBiclik-unsplash_gy44ix_exacii\" data-image=\"ai-generated-0\" alt=\"\">\n                                </figure></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>The Power of Your Inner Healer</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Your <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/discover-your-inner-healer-a-guide-to-holistic-healing-and-breathwork\">inner </a><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/discover-your-inner-healer-a-guide-to-holistic-healing-and-breathwork\">healer</a> is that innate ability within you to help your body heal itself. <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">it\'s</a> not some mystical force, but a scientifically recognized concept backed by our understanding of the body\'s incredible capacity for self-repair. You\'ve probably experienced your inner healer in action without even realizing it – like when a minor cut heals itself, or when you bounce back from a cold.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>But tapping into this <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/healthy-masculinity-the-power-of-mens-groups-in-collective-healing\">power</a> on a deeper level requires a more conscious approach. This is where holistic healing comes into play.</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Embracing Holistic Healing</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>When we talk about \'holistic healing\', we\'re talking about a whole-person approach to health and wellbeing. It\'s not just about treating symptoms or diseases, but about addressing the root cause of issues and promoting overall wellness. This method respects the interconnectedness of your body, mind, and spirit, and it aims to bring <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/breathe-your-way-to-balance-the-polyvagal-theory-and-meditation\">balance</a> to all these aspects of your <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">life</a>.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>For example, a holistic approach might involve dietary changes, physical activity, stress management, and even spiritual practices. It\'s a versatile, personalized approach that can enhance your overall quality of life.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Exploring Breathwork Therapy Techniques</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>One of the most profound techniques to awaken your inner healer is <a href=\"https://melbournebreathwork.com\">breathwork</a>. Breathwork is a broad term for various practices that use conscious and controlled breathing to improve mental, physical, and spiritual health.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>It might seem simple, but don\'t be fooled. These techniques can have a powerful effect. They can help you manage stress, improve mental clarity, and even accelerate physical healing. Plus, they can be practiced anywhere, anytime, making them a highly accessible tool for wellness.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>So, whether you\'re looking to improve your overall health, manage a specific condition, or simply explore new ways to relax and rejuvenate, consider tapping into your inner healer. Through holistic healing and breathwork, you might discover a whole new level of wellness and self-empowerment. Remember, the journey to health is a personal one, so embrace the process with an open mind and heart.</p></div>\n                        </div></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2025-07-11 22:37:03', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'meagan-carsience-TpG2TBiclik-unsplash_gy44ix_exacii', 1314, 1, 'Explore the concept of the \'inner healer\' and discover how holistic healing and breathwork therapy techniques can help you unlock your body\'s innate healing potential.', 'Unlock Your Inner Healer: Guide to Holistic Healing &amp; Breathwork', NULL, 'Explore the power of your inner healer through a holistic approach and breathwork. Understand your body\'s capacity for self-repair, manage stress, improve mental clarity, and enhance the quality of your life.', '2025-07-11 22:37:03', '2026-01-05 00:10:30', 4, 1, 64, NULL, 0, 61, NULL, 0, ''),
	(3071, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'The Science Behind Breath Holding &amp; Over Breathing', 'the-science-behind-breath-holding-over-breathing', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative redactor-component-active\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span class=\"redactor-component-caret\">﻿</span>\n                                    <img class=\"fb-image-white-border-large\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/q_70/f_auto/r_0/1314/jeremy-bishop-ewkxn5capa4-unsplashjpg-jmha5thr\" data-image=\"ai-generated-0\" alt=\"\">\n                                </figure></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>A Deep Dive into Breath Holding &amp; Over Breathing</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>Unpacking the Physiology of Breath Holding</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>When you hold your breath, your body undergoes several physiological changes. Initially, the oxygen level in your blood decreases, while carbon dioxide levels rise. This increase in carbon dioxide can trigger a feeling of discomfort or even panic. <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">it\'s</a> your body\'s way of saying, \'Hey, we need more oxygen over here!\'</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>But, if you continue to hold your breath, your body begins to adapt. It\'s a survival mechanism, really. Your heart rate may slow down, helping to conserve oxygen. This is known as the \'diving reflex\', and it\'s particularly noticeable if you\'re holding your breath while underwater.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>Over Breathing: More than Just a Lot of Air</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Now, on to over breathing. You might think that taking in extra air would be a good thing, right? Well, not necessarily. Over breathing - also known as hyperventilation - can lead to too much oxygen and too little carbon dioxide in the blood. This imbalance can cause symptoms like lightheadedness, tingling in the hands or feet, and rapid heartbeat.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Interestingly, over breathing can be both a physical response to stress or anxiety, and a cause of these feelings. It\'s a bit of a vicious cycle. When you\'re feeling stressed, you might start to breathe more rapidly. This over breathing then leads to physical symptoms, which can make you feel even more anxious.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Both breath holding and over breathing show us just how connected our breath is to our overall <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/appointments\">health</a> and well-being. So, next time you take a big gulp of air, remember there\'s a lot more going on than meets the eye!</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2025-08-03 23:45:54', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'jeremy-bishop-ewkxn5capa4-unsplashjpg-jmha5thr', 1314, 1, 'Discover the physiological changes that occur when you hold your breath or over breathe. Understand the connection between your breathing patterns and overall health.', 'The Science Behind Breath Holding &amp; Over Breathing', NULL, '', '2025-08-03 23:45:54', '2025-08-03 23:47:52', 4, 1, 66, '2025-08-03 23:47:52', 0, 64, NULL, 0, ''),
	(3072, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'Breathe Your Way to Health: The Power of Wim Hof\'s Breath Holding Technique', 'breathe-your-way-to-health-the-power-of-wim-hofs-breath-holding-technique', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                                    <img class=\"\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/v1754264612/1314/mark-basarab-1otukd-8svc-unsplashjpg-parnvgwq.jpg\" data-image=\"ai-generated-0\">\n                                </figure></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p align=\"right\">Take a deep <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/home\">breath</a>, hold it, and let it out slowly. You\'ve just performed one of the simplest exercises with some of the most profound health benefits. But have you ever wondered just what happens during that breath hold and how it contributes to your health?</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2 align=\"right\">Breath Hold Health Benefits: More Than Just a Pause</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p align=\"right\">Breath holding isn\'t merely a pause in the respiratory process. <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">it\'s</a> a dynamic period that sets off a series of chemical changes in your body. These changes, as we\'ll see, can play a significant role in stress reduction and overall health improvement.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3 align=\"right\">Chemical Changes During Breath Holding</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p align=\"right\">When you hold your breath, the <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/breathe-your-way-to-balance-the-polyvagal-theory-and-meditation\">balance</a> of oxygen and carbon dioxide in your body shifts. Oxygen levels decrease, while carbon dioxide levels increase, causing your body to react in ways that can have positive effects on your health. For instance, this chemical change can boost your immune response, increase your mental clarity, and even enhance your athletic performance.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2 align=\"right\">The Wim Hof Method: Breathing for Health and Stress Reduction</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p align=\"right\">Wim Hof, also known as \'The Iceman\', has harnessed the <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/healthy-masculinity-the-power-of-mens-groups-in-collective-healing\">power</a> of breath holding in a technique that bears his name. The Wim Hof Method combines breath holding with cold exposure and <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/breathe-your-way-to-balance-the-polyvagal-theory-and-meditation\">meditation</a> to create a powerful tool for stress reduction and health improvement. </p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3 align=\"right\">Practising the Wim Hof Method</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p align=\"right\">Practising the Wim Hof Method begins with a series of deep breaths followed by a breath hold. The length of the breath hold gradually increases as you progress in your practice, helping your body adapt to the chemical changes and reaping more health benefits. The technique also includes meditation and exposure to cold, which further enhances the effects of breath holding.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p align=\"right\">So, the next time you\'re feeling stressed or just looking for a simple way to boost your health, take a moment to hold your breath. Your body and mind will thank you for it!</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2025-08-03 23:48:45', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'mark-basarab-1otukd-8svc-unsplashjpg-parnvgwq', 1314, 1, 'Explore the health benefits of breath holding, the chemical changes it induces, and how the Wim Hof Method harnesses these for stress reduction.', '', NULL, '', '2025-08-03 23:48:45', '2025-08-03 23:49:44', 4, 1, 66, '2025-08-03 23:49:44', 0, 64, NULL, 0, ''),
	(3073, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'The Harmonious Connection Between Breathwork, Music, and Trance', 'the-harmonious-connection-between-breathwork-music-and-trance', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\">\n                                <figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                                    <img class=\"\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/v1751524556/1314/IMG_0349_dxl0mm.jpg\" data-image=\"ai-generated-0\">\n                                </figure>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Understanding the Power of Breathwork</h2></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\">\n                                <figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                                    <img class=\"\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/v1751524556/1314/IMG_0349_dxl0mm.jpg\" data-image=\"ai-generated-1\">\n                                </figure>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Music: The Universal Language of Emotion</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Music has an undeniable emotional impact. It\'s like a universal language that doesn\'t need words to be understood. It can make us feel happy, sad, energized, or calm. It has the power to take us back in time, make us dance, or even put us to sleep. This emotional connection between music and us is something that can be harnessed for better <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">mental health</a>.</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\">\n                                <figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                                    <img class=\"\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/v1751524556/1314/IMG_0349_dxl0mm.jpg\" data-image=\"ai-generated-2\">\n                                </figure>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Trance: A State of Heightened Consciousness</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Trance is a state of mind that is often associated with deep meditation or hypnosis. But it\'s actually a natural state that we all experience from time to time. Ever been so absorbed in a book or a movie that you lost track of time? That\'s a form of trance. It\'s a state of heightened focus and reduced peripheral awareness.</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\">\n                                <figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                                    <img class=\"\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/v1751524556/1314/IMG_0349_dxl0mm.jpg\" data-image=\"ai-generated-3\">\n                                </figure>\n                            </div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Interweaving Breathwork, Music, and Trance</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>So, what happens when we combine breathwork, music, and trance? We get a powerful method for self-<a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/discover-your-inner-healer-a-guide-to-holistic-healing-and-breathwork\">healing</a> and self-exploration. Breathwork can guide us into a trance state, and music can amplify the emotional experience. It\'s like a symphony where breathwork is the conductor, music is the orchestra, and trance is the beautiful music they create.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>Experience It for Yourself</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Reading about it is one thing, but experiencing it is entirely different. I encourage you to try a guided breathwork session with music. You might be surprised at how transformative it can be.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3 class=\'mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\'>Possibly Related Content</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">Holotropic Breathwork &amp; it\'s potential life changing impact</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/services/holotropic-breathwork\">Holotropic Breathwork</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/unlocking-the-power-of-breathwork-impact-on-the-central-nervous-system\">Unlocking the Power of Breathwork: Impact on the Central Nervous System</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/services/mens-groups\">Mens Groups</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources\">Resources</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3 class=\'mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\'>Upcoming events</h3></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>\n\n', '2025-08-04 02:04:53', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'IMG_0349_dxl0mm', 1314, 1, 'This article explores the fascinating intersection of breathwork, music, and trance, and how they can be combined for enhanced emotional and physical health.', '', NULL, '', '2025-08-04 02:04:53', '2025-08-04 02:05:29', 4, 1, 66, '2025-08-04 02:05:29', 1, 64, NULL, 0, NULL),
	(3074, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'The Magic of Breathwork and Music: A Journey into Trance', 'the-magic-of-breathwork-and-music-a-journey-into-trance', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                                    <img class=\"\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/v1754264634/1314/jeremy-bishop-ewkxn5capa4-unsplashjpg-jmha5thr.jpg\" data-image=\"ai-generated-0\">\n                                </figure></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>The Incredible Fusion of Breathwork and Music</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>What is Breathwork?</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Simply put, breathwork is the practice of using conscious and controlled breathing techniques to enhance mental, physical, and spiritual well-being. It\'s not a newfangled idea either; our ancestors have been harnessing the power of the breath for centuries. From yogic pranayama to the Holotropic breathwork of modern psychology, this practice is as varied as it is ancient.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>Music: A Universal Language of Emotion</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Music, on the other hand, transcends borders, cultures, and time itself. It\'s a universal language that speaks straight to the heart. Whether it\'s a heart-pounding rock concert or a tranquil symphony, music has the power to move us on a profound, emotional level.</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>When Breathwork Meets Music</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Merging breathwork with music can create a deep, immersive experience. The rhythm and melody of the music guide your breath, leading to a harmonious dance between the two. This synergy can help you dive deeper into your subconscious, allowing for self-reflection and <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/discover-your-inner-healer-a-guide-to-holistic-healing-and-breathwork\">healing</a>.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>Entering the Trance State</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>As you surrender to the rhythm of your breath and the soundscapes, you may find yourself slipping into a trance-like state. This is not something to fear, but rather, an opportunity for deep introspection and <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">personal</a> growth. It\'s a state where our conscious mind takes a backseat, and our subconscious mind comes to the fore, often revealing insights and emotions we might not confront in our daily lives.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>The Potential Benefits</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>The combination of breathwork, music, and trance can lead to various benefits. These include stress reduction, increased self-awareness, emotional release, and even profound spiritual experiences. However, like any practice, it\'s important to approach it with an open mind and respect for the process.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3 class=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\">Possibly Related Content</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">Holotropic Breathwork &amp; it\'s potential life changing impact</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/services/holotropic-breathwork\">Holotropic Breathwork</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/discover-your-inner-healer-a-guide-to-holistic-healing-and-breathwork\">Discover Your Inner Healer: A Guide to Holistic Healing and Breathwork</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/home\">Home</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/unlocking-the-power-of-breathwork-impact-on-the-central-nervous-system\">Unlocking the Power of Breathwork: Impact on the Central Nervous System</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3 class=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\">Upcoming Events</h3><p>﻿﻿﻿{%feed|domain:melbournebreathwork.com|model:events|filter:future|layout:calendar%}</p></div>\n                        </div></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2025-08-04 02:09:10', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'jeremy-bishop-ewkxn5capa4-unsplashjpg-jmha5thr', 1314, 1, 'Explore the powerful combination of breathwork and music, and learn how it can lead to trance states for deep healing and personal growth.', '', NULL, '', '2025-08-04 02:09:10', '2025-08-04 02:11:58', 4, 1, 66, '2025-08-04 02:11:58', 0, 64, NULL, 0, ''),
	(3076, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'The Rise of Men\'s Groups: Fostering Emotional Intelligence and Personal Growth', 'the-rise-of-mens-groups-fostering-emotional-intelligence-and-personal-growth', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative\" tabindex=\"-1\">\n                                    <img class=\"\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/v1751337716/1314/meagan-carsience-TpG2TBiclik-unsplash_gy44ix_exacii.jpg\" data-image=\"ai-generated-1\">\n                                </figure></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Understanding the Role of Men\'s Groups</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>So, what exactly are men\'s groups? Well, they\'re not your typical \'boys\' night out\'. Instead, these are gatherings where men come together to discuss their feelings, challenges, and aspirations. It\'s not about \'fixing\' each other, but rather, it\'s about creating an environment of acceptance, understanding, and mutual support.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>The Power of Emotional Intelligence</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>One of the key aspects that men\'s groups emphasize is the development of emotional intelligence. This involves understanding and managing one\'s own emotions, as well as being able to empathize with others. It\'s about breaking free from the \'man up\' mentality and embracing the fact that it\'s okay for men to be emotionally vulnerable.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>Fostering Personal Growth</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Men\'s groups also provide a platform for <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">personal growth</a>. They challenge men to step out of their comfort zones, confront their fears, and strive for self-improvement. From improving communication skills to enhancing self-esteem, the benefits are truly life-changing.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3 class=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\">Possibly Related Content</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/healthy-masculinity-the-power-of-mens-groups-in-collective-healing\">Healthy Masculinity: The Power of Men\'s Groups in Collective Healing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/services/mens-groups\">Mens Groups</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">Holotropic Breathwork &amp; it\'s potential life changing impact</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/home\">Home</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/holotropic-breathwork-a-journey-into-healing-and-understanding-body-physiology\">Holotropic Breathwork: A Journey into Healing and Understanding Body Physiology</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2025-08-04 02:13:10', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'meagan-carsience-TpG2TBiclik-unsplash_gy44ix_exacii', 1314, 1, 'An exploration of men\'s groups, their role in promoting emotional intelligence, and fostering personal growth. Understand the significance of these groups in redefining masculinity.', 'The Rise of Men\'s Groups: Fostering Emotional Intelligence and Personal Growth', NULL, 'An exploration of men\'s groups, their role in promoting emotional intelligence, and fostering personal growth. Understand the significance of these groups in redefining masculinity.', '2025-08-04 02:13:10', '2026-01-05 00:10:30', 4, 1, 68, NULL, 0, 62, NULL, 0, ''),
	(3077, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'The Tranquil Symmetry: Breathwork Meets Music', 'the-tranquil-symmetry-breathwork-meets-music', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative redactor-component-active\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span class=\"redactor-component-caret\">﻿</span>\n                                    <img class=\"fb-image-white-border-large\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/q_70/f_auto/r_0/1314/damiano-baschiera-d4feocyfzam-unsplashjpg-ppzomws0\" data-image=\"ai-generated-2\" alt=\"\">\n                                </figure></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>The Rhythm of Music</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Like breathwork, music has a rhythm and a beat. It sets the tempo, and our bodies often respond instinctively. Ever found yourself tapping your foot or clapping your hands to a catchy tune? That\'s your body syncing with the music. This connection can be harnessed in powerful ways to promote <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/discover-your-inner-healer-a-guide-to-holistic-healing-and-breathwork\">healing</a> and well-being.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Breathwork and Music: A Harmonious Blend</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>When you combine breathwork with music, something truly special happens. The rhythm of the music can guide your breath, helping to steady it and create a calming effect. This combination can lead to a trance-like state, where you\'re deeply connected with your own emotions and thoughts. It\'s like embarking on a journey of self-discovery and healing.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>Creating Your Breathwork Music Playlist</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Choosing the right music for your breathwork practice is important. Look for songs with a steady, rhythmic beat that matches the pace of your breathing. It\'s also a good idea to select music that resonates with you emotionally. After all, this is a deeply <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/the-rise-of-mens-groups-fostering-emotional-intelligence-and-personal-growth\">personal</a> practice, and what works for one <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/appointments\">person</a> may not work for another.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>Experiencing a Breathwork Music Trance</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>When you enter a trance-like state through breathwork and music, you\'re opening yourself up to a deeper level of self-awareness. It\'s a state where healing can occur, where you can confront feelings and emotions that you\'ve perhaps been avoiding. It\'s not always an easy journey, but it\'s one that can lead to profound transformation.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3 class=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\">Possibly Related Content</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">Holotropic Breathwork &amp; it\'s potential life changing impact</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/discover-your-inner-healer-a-guide-to-holistic-healing-and-breathwork\">Discover Your Inner Healer: A Guide to Holistic Healing and Breathwork</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/services/holotropic-breathwork\">Holotropic Breathwork</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/unlocking-the-power-of-breathwork-impact-on-the-central-nervous-system\">Unlocking the Power of Breathwork: Impact on the Central Nervous System</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/home\">Home</a></li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<h3>Upcoming Events</h3>\n<p>﻿﻿﻿{%feed|domain:melbournebreathwork.com|model:events|filter:future|layout:calendar%}</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2025-08-04 02:15:48', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'damiano-baschiera-d4feocyfzam-unsplashjpg-ppzomws0', 1314, 1, 'Unravel the unique combination of breathwork and music, how it can induce a trance, and its potential for deeper self-understanding and healing.', 'Harnessing the Power of Breathwork and Music for Healing', NULL, 'Discover the harmonious blend of breathwork and music for health and well-being. Embark on a personal journey of self-discovery and profound transformation through our rhythm-guided practices.', '2025-08-04 02:15:48', '2026-01-05 00:10:30', 4, 1, 69, NULL, 0, 63, NULL, 0, ''),
	(3093, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'Sessions now available on the Surf Coast', 'the-tranquil-symmetry-breathwork-meets-music-1pht', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large row-columns-1-3_2-3 with-redo\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-3@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative redactor-component-active\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span class=\"redactor-component-caret\">﻿</span>\n                                    <img class=\"fb-image-white-border-large\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/q_70/f_auto/r_0/1314/andrew-st-lawrence-w0v2678-r-w-unsplash_vqkhgz\" data-image=\"ai-generated-2\" alt=\"\">\n                                </figure></div>\n                        </div>\n                    <div class=\"uk-width-1-1 content-block\">\n    <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/appointments/lorne\" class=\"uk-button btn uk-button-primary\">BOOK A SESSION ON THE SURF COAST</a>﻿</p></div>\n</div></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-2-3@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        \n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2 data-redactor-style-cache=\"margin: 0px;\" style=\"margin: 0px;\">From February 2026, I will be offering psychotherapy and one-to-one breathwork sessions in Lorne on the Surf Coast of Victoria.</h2>\n<p>﻿Alongside my Melbourne practice in Brunswick, this expands my work into the surrounds of the Erskine River rainforest, providing a quieter regional setting for depth-oriented psychotherapy and individual breathwork.</p>\n<p>I have had a longstanding relationship with Lorne and the Surf Coast, returning regularly for over three decades. I now have the opportunity to spend extended time living and working here, allowing my clinical practice to be shaped more directly by our relationship with place and the natural environment.</p>\n<p>Working in a coastal and forested setting offers something distinct from urban practice. Proximity to nature often supports a slower rhythm, greater embodied awareness, and a broader psychological perspective. Where appropriate, psychotherapy in Lorne may also draw on breathwork and nature-based or eco-therapy approaches, supporting a deeper connection to bodily experience and the natural world.﻿</p>\n<figure class=\"\" tabindex=\"-1\" style=\"box-sizing: border-box; border: 0px solid; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; width: 736px;\"><hr></figure>\n<h2>Approach and Modalities offered:</h2>\n<ul><li><strong><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/services/psychotherapy-and-counselling\">Psychotherapy</a></strong><br>Depth-oriented, trauma-informed psychotherapy for individuals, drawing on relational and embodied approaches.<br>﻿</li><li><strong><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/services/holotropic-breathwork\">One-to-one breathwork</a></strong><br>Individual breathwork sessions offered within a therapeutic framework, supporting emotional processing and nervous system regulation.</li><li><strong>Breath based somatic approaches <br>﻿</strong>Attention to bodily experience as part of psychological work, supporting integration and embodied awareness.</li><li><strong>Nature-based and eco-therapy approaches</strong><br>Where appropriate, therapeutic work may incorporate the natural environment as a supportive context for reflection and regulation.</li><li><strong>Integration-oriented work</strong><br>Support for integrating expanded, altered, or non-ordinary states of consciousness within a grounded psychotherapeutic framework.</li></ul></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2026-01-01 02:15:48', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'andrew-st-lawrence-w0v2678-r-w-unsplash_vqkhgz', 1314, 1, 'From February 2026, I will be offering psychotherapy and one-to-one breathwork sessions in Lorne on the Surf Coast of Victoria.', 'Psychotherapy & Breathwork Sessions in Lorne, Surf Coast - Victoria', NULL, 'Offering depth-oriented psychotherapy and individual breathwork sessions in the serene setting of Lorne, Surf Coast from February 2026. Experience a therapeutical journey amidst nature, supporting emotional processing, nervous system regulation, and eco-therapy approaches.', '2026-01-02 04:59:36', '2026-01-05 00:10:30', 4, 1, 73, NULL, 0, 64, NULL, 0, ''),
	(3098, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'Harness the Power of Breath for Relaxation and Healing', 'harness-the-power-of-breath-for-relaxation-and-healing', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large row-columns-1-3_2-3\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-3@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative redactor-component-active\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span class=\"redactor-component-caret\">﻿</span>\n                                    <img class=\"fb-image-white-border-large\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/q_70/f_auto/r_0/1314/Brunswick_Room_w89mkd\" data-image=\"ai-generated-1\" alt=\"\">\n                                </figure></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-2-3@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        \n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h1>The Science Behind Deep Breathing and Relaxation</h1></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>When you\'re stressed or anxious, your body enters a state of \'fight or flight.\' In contrast, deep, mindful breathing can help your body transition to a state of relaxation. This change happens because deep breathing stimulates the vagus nerve, a key player in your body\'s parasympathetic <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/unlocking-the-power-of-breathwork-impact-on-the-central-nervous-system\">nervous system</a>, which controls rest and digestion.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Healing Trauma with Breath</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>For those recovering from trauma, particularly trauma that\'s impacted the <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/unlocking-the-power-of-breathwork-impact-on-the-central-nervous-system\">central nervous</a> system, deep breathing can be a game-changer. It\'s a way of signaling to your body that it\'s safe to relax and start the healing process. A study published in the \'Journal of Alternative and Complementary Medicine\' found that survivors of physical trauma who practised deep, mindful breathing showed significant improvements in symptoms related to post-traumatic stress disorder (PTSD).</p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Practical Breathing Exercises for Relaxation and Healing</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>Let me share with you a simple yet effective deep breathing exercise that I often recommend. It\'s called \'Box Breathing.\'</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h2>Box Breathing</h2></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><ol><li>Exhale all the air in your lungs through your mouth.</li><li>Close your mouth and quietly inhale through your nose to a mental count of four.</li><li>Hold your breath for a count of four.</li><li>Exhale through your mouth for a count of four.</li><li>Hold your breath for a count of four.</li><li>Repeat the process.</li></ol></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><p>By practicing these exercises daily, you can tap into the innate power of your <a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/about\">breath</a>, promoting relaxation and facilitating healing.</p></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3 class=\"mt-4 pt-4 border-t border-gray-100\">Possibly Related Content</h3></div>\n                        </div><div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/breathe-your-way-to-balance-the-polyvagal-theory-and-meditation\">Breathe Your Way to Balance: The Polyvagal Theory and Meditation</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/unlocking-the-power-of-breathwork-impact-on-the-central-nervous-system\">Unlocking the Power of Breathwork: Impact on the Central Nervous System</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/discover-your-inner-healer-a-guide-to-holistic-healing-and-breathwork\">Discover Your Inner Healer: A Guide to Holistic Healing and Breathwork</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/healthy-masculinity-the-power-of-mens-groups-in-collective-healing\">Healthy Masculinity: The Power of Men\'s Groups in Collective Healing</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://wildheartpsychotherapy.com.au/resources/holotropic-breathwork-its-potential-life-changing-impact\">Holotropic Breathwork &amp; it\'s potential life changing impact</a></li>\n</ul></div>\n                        </div></div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2026-01-05 00:57:39', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'Brunswick_Room_w89mkd', 1314, 1, 'This article explores the science-backed benefits of mindful breathing for relaxation and healing, especially for those recovering from central nervous system trauma.', 'Harness the Power of Breath for Relaxation and Healing', NULL, '', '2026-01-05 00:57:39', '2026-01-05 00:59:21', 4, 1, 77, NULL, 0, 70, NULL, 0, ''),
	(3105, 1314, 857, 1314, 1314, 1, 'Can AI do therapy and is it an existential risk?', 'can-ai-do-therapy-and-is-it-an-existential-risk', '<div class=\"content-row uk-position-relative uk-flex padding-large with-redo\">\n    <div class=\"uk-container\">\n        <div class=\"uk-grid\">\n            <div class=\"uk-width-1-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><figure class=\"uk-margin-remove-top uk-position-relative redactor-component-active\" tabindex=\"-1\"><span class=\"redactor-component-caret\">﻿</span>\n                                    <img class=\"fb-image-white-border-large\" src=\"https://res.cloudinary.com/feelbettr/image/upload/q_70/f_auto/r_0/1314/florian-van-duyn-dm-qxdynoec-unsplashjpg-sprqsbls\" data-image=\"ai-generated-1\" alt=\"\">\n                                </figure></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n            <div class=\"uk-width-3-4@m uk-position-relative\">\n                <div class=\"grid-inner\">\n                    <div class=\"uk-sortable\">\n                        <h1 class=\"font-bold mb-4\">{%title%}</h1>\n                        <div class=\"content-block\">\n                            <div class=\"content-block-inner\"><h3>I\'ve been thinking a bit recently (like many people) about what role artificial intelligence will play in the future for psychotherapy. So I thought I&nbsp;﻿would ask one of the LLM\'s what it thought about it. The answer was not surprising in that it detailed the obvious high points and low points of the impact that AI will have on psychotherapy, but missed the important area of \"alignment\". What is the aim of psychotherapy and who are we doing this for?&nbsp;</h3><p>As with most technologies they can represent a huge advancement and help for humanity if they are used well ... and this last part is entirely subjective and easy to be manipulated as we have seen with some <a href=\"https://www.bbc.com/news/articles/ce3xgwyywe4o\">disturbing high profile international cases</a>. So we will wait and see what the consequences are but thought you may enjoy reading this below.﻿<b><br></b></p>\n<p><b>What are the existential threat to psychotherapists and AI? My sense is that LLM can do perhaps 80% of the heavy lifting when it comes to understanding, affirming, distilling etc but it\'s not currently capable of the co-regulation that is really underneath the therapeutic interaction. Or is it capable of that? and if it is what does that mean for the future of psychotherapy?</b></p>\n<p>Your intuition is actually very close to where a lot of serious discussion about AI and psychotherapy currently sits. The key distinction many clinicians and researchers make is <strong>cognition vs regulation</strong>.</p>\n<p>AI is getting very good at the <strong>cognitive layer</strong> of therapy, but psychotherapy is arguably grounded in <strong>nervous-system interaction</strong>.</p>\n<p>Let’s break it down.</p>\n<h1>1. What AI can already do surprisingly well in therapy</h1>\n<p>Large language models can already perform much of the <strong>explicit cognitive work</strong> therapists do:</p>\n<p><strong>Understanding</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>summarising narratives</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>identifying patterns</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>recognising emotional language</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Reflective responses</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>paraphrasing</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>empathic language</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>validation</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Conceptual framing</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>CBT reframing</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>attachment interpretations</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>psychoeducation</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Practical support</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>journaling prompts</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>behavioural plans</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>cognitive restructuring</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Apps like Wysa, Woebot, and Replika already do versions of this.</p>\n<p>For many people with mild anxiety or loneliness, these tools already provide <strong>meaningful psychological support</strong>.</p>\n<p>So your <strong>“80% of the cognitive heavy lifting”</strong> estimate is not unreasonable.</p>\n<h1>2. The core thing psychotherapy may rely on: co-regulation</h1>\n<p>Where your intuition becomes very important is <strong>co-regulation</strong>.</p>\n<p>Modern neuroscience (especially interpersonal neurobiology and polyvagal theory) suggests that therapy works through:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>nervous system attunement</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>safety signals</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>facial expression</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>tone of voice</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>breathing synchrony</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>micro-timing of response</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Key figures discussing this include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>Stephen Porges</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Allan Schore</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>Daniel Siegel</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>The idea is that <strong>healing happens partly through regulated relational presence</strong>, not just insight.</p>\n<p>A client’s nervous system literally <strong>settles in the presence of a regulated other human</strong>.</p>\n<p>That’s something text alone cannot do.</p>\n<h1>3. Can AI do co-regulation?</h1>\n<p>Currently: <strong>not really.</strong></p>\n<p>But it depends on what we mean.</p>\n<h3>AI can simulate emotional attunement</h3>\n<p>It can generate language like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>“That sounds painful.”</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>“It makes sense you feel that way.”</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This can feel supportive, but it’s <strong>symbolic empathy</strong>, not physiological attunement.</p>\n<h3>Real co-regulation involves physiology</h3>\n<p>True co-regulation often includes:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>eye contact</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>micro facial expressions</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>vocal prosody</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>breathing rhythm</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>embodied presence</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Even on Zoom some of this is lost.</p>\n<p>With text AI, <strong>almost all of it disappears</strong>.</p>\n<h3>However, partial regulation may still occur</h3>\n<p>Humans can self-regulate through:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>writing</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>reflection</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>journaling</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>structured thinking</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>AI can facilitate those processes.</p>\n<p>So it may act more like:</p>\n<p><strong>a cognitive scaffolding for self-regulation.</strong></p>\n<h1>4. Where AI might become much more powerful</h1>\n<p>The picture changes if AI is combined with <strong>embodied interfaces</strong>.</p>\n<p>For example:</p>\n<p>Future systems could include:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>voice with emotional prosody</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>facial expression recognition</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>physiological monitoring</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>real-time nervous system feedback</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Imagine a system that tracks:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>heart rate variability</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>voice stress</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>breathing patterns</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Then adjusts its responses accordingly.</p>\n<p>At that point AI could begin approximating <strong>regulation feedback loops</strong>.</p>\n<p>Still not human — but closer.</p>\n<h1>5. The likely future structure of psychotherapy</h1>\n<p>Most analysts think psychotherapy will split into <strong>three layers</strong>.</p>\n<h3>Layer 1 — AI mental health support (mass scale)</h3>\n<p>For:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>mild anxiety</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>loneliness</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>journaling</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>emotional reflection</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>psychoeducation</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Accessible 24/7.</p>\n<p>Huge global impact.</p>\n<h3>Layer 2 — AI-augmented therapy</h3>\n<p>Therapists using AI for:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>session summarisation</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>pattern detection</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>treatment planning</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>progress tracking</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>You already see early tools like Eleos Health doing this.</p>\n<h3>Layer 3 — high-value relational therapy</h3>\n<p>Where human therapists remain essential:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>trauma work</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>attachment repair</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>complex personality dynamics</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>embodied regulation</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>transference/countertransference</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>psychedelic therapy</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>deep existential work</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>This is <strong>the part least replaceable</strong>.</p>\n<h1>6. Why psychotherapy may actually become more valuable</h1>\n<p>Paradoxically, AI may increase demand for <strong>real human therapeutic presence</strong>.</p>\n<p>Because AI interactions may highlight the difference between:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>simulated empathy</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>genuine relational presence</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Much like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>streaming music increased demand for live concerts</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>social media increased desire for in-person community</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1>7. A deeper point relevant to your work</h1>\n<p>Given your involvement with breathwork and expanded states, there’s an additional layer.</p>\n<p>Practices like:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>breathwork</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>psychedelic therapy</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>somatic therapy</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>depend heavily on:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>embodied presence</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>energetic attunement</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>nervous system resonance</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>These are <strong>far harder to digitise</strong>.</p>\n<p>The more therapy moves toward <strong>state work rather than talk work</strong>, the harder it is to automate.</p>\n<h1>8. The real existential threat to psychotherapy</h1>\n<p>The biggest risk probably isn\'t replacement.</p>\n<p>It’s <strong>commodification of emotional support</strong>.</p>\n<p>Cheap AI systems could become the <strong>default mental health interface for billions of people</strong>.</p>\n<p>Human therapy could become:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>\n<p>more specialised</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>more expensive</p>\n</li>\n<li>\n<p>more niche</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p>But also potentially <strong>more valued</strong>.</p>\n<p>✅ <strong>Your core intuition is strong:</strong></p>\n<p>LLMs may replace much of the <strong>verbal processing layer</strong> of therapy.</p>\n<p>But psychotherapy may ultimately rest on <strong>co-regulation and embodied relational presence</strong>, which is far harder to replicate.﻿<br></p></div>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </div>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"content-row-overlay\"></div>\n</div>', '2026-03-06 07:08:50', NULL, 0, '1', '', 'florian-van-duyn-dm-qxdynoec-unsplashjpg-sprqsbls', 1314, 1, 'Holotropic breathwork, a therapy technique often used in mental health treatment programs, is a unique method to achieve heightened self-awareness and personal growth. It employs a combination of rapid, deep breathing, evocative music, and focused bodywork to stimulate the psyche and bring about emotional release and psychological insight.', 'Holotropic Breathwork for Mental Health and Personal Growth', NULL, 'Explore how Holotropic Breathwork, a unique therapeutic technique, can facilitate personal growth and improve mental health by activating your inner healer. Learn about its benefits and how to start your journey.', '2026-03-06 01:52:30', '2026-03-06 02:00:20', 4, 1, 78, NULL, 0, 71, NULL, 0, '');
